{"tid":785320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"6歲童患罕病面容如80歲　母泣：生給你這張臉是我的錯","createTime":"2018-08-19T06:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T18:33:09.000Z","uid":49391,"like":123,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d5d9ad79095766f5f419d0c6da2b1c0f78d3e3","tid":785320,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:22:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0h1AjNSiZNbm5XN0NxYGoROW1hbQFkW31tMwE_bRRZMFopASA6O1BxAHQwMVcoUCkwOQYkDnMwdV9zVCw_agZx/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0h1AjNSiZNbm5XN0NxYGoROW1hbQFkW31tMwE_bRRZMFopASA6O1BxAHQwMVcoUCkwOQYkDnMwdV9zVCw_agZx%2Fw644&h=8ab76b1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n令人鼻酸！一名哈薩克的6歲男童，因得了先天性罕見疾病，導致在嬌小的身軀裡，有著鬆垮的皮膚，體內的關節、脊椎等甚至開始萎縮&hellip;讓他的母親難過表示「我真不希望他長大」。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，這名6歲男童名叫Yernar Alibekov，他患有先天性結締組織發育不全綜合症，他在出生一個月後，臉部皮膚開始衰老，遍布皺紋，眼皮周遭、臉頰、下巴等皮膚也都迅速鬆弛，惡化速度相當快！<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此Yernar連體內也隨著年紀增長，還患有關節炎，如同老人般，脊椎退化、關節疼痛萎縮，雖然家人們經常陪伴在Yernar身邊、逗他開心，但隨著Yernar愈來愈大，每當他外出時，總是得承受外人的異樣眼光，他自己也慢慢開始害怕出門、與人交際。<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hzA17noweJW4MTghxOOdaOTYYJgE_IjZtaHh0bU8ge1pyeGs6OH8-AC9KKAopKmIwYn9vDSFNPl8oLWc_MXw-/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hzA17noweJW4MTghxOOdaOTYYJgE_IjZtaHh0bU8ge1pyeGs6OH8-AC9KKAopKmIwYn9vDSFNPl8oLWc_MXw-%2Fw644&h=94ddafee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYernar家中經濟狀況並不富裕，家族成員們已為Yernar的治療費用四處奔波、到處借錢，卻還是趕不上Yernar衰老的速度。他的母親難過地表示「很自責生給兒子一張這樣的臉蛋，我真不希望他長大」。<br />\n<br />\nYernar的家人目前也正在籌錢，讓Yernar接受整容手術，不過根據哈薩克政府官方法規，民眾必須年滿18歲才可以接受整容手術，且醫學專家曾對Yernar一家人直言「Yernar就算長大後接受整容手術，也無法根治這項先天性的疾病，術後成效恐怕沒有太大希望。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/tw/pc/article/6%E6%AD%B2%E7%AB%A5%E6%82%A3%E7%BD%95%E7%97%85%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%B9%E5%A6%8280%E6%AD%B2%E3%80%80%E6%AF%8D%E6%B3%A3%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%9F%E7%B5%A6%E4%BD%A0%E9%80%99%E5%BC%B5%E8%87%89%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E9%8C%AF-VZwp3y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Ftw%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F6%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%2582%25A3%25E7%25BD%2595%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E5%25A6%258280%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E3%2580%2580%25E6%25AF%258D%25E6%25B3%25A3%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%2587%2589%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%258C%25AF-VZwp3y&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5n26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f7bb33c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/tw/pc/article/6%E6%AD%B2%E7%AB%A5%E6%82%A3%E7%BD%95%E7%97%85%E9%9D%A2%E5%AE%B9%E5%A6%8280%E6%AD%B2%E3%80%80%E6%AF%8D%E6%B3%A3%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%9F%E7%B5%A6%E4%BD%A0%E9%80%99%E5%BC%B5%E8%87%89%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E9%8C%AF-VZwp3y</a>"},{"pid":"e21add7a74cb0e4ad1532a218686c07458dd47e1","tid":785320,"uid":49391,"like":324,"dislike":4,"score":320,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:22:36.000Z","msg":"奇幻逆緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94844e4de8995c581ba8473efae18f0602f3a35b","tid":785320,"uid":83328,"like":194,"dislike":4,"score":190,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"應該愈大愈後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd508128c6057c0821c08187f842e085ac8c2d6","tid":785320,"uid":146535,"like":4,"dislike":20,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"e21add7a74cb0e4ad1532a218686c07458dd47e1","tid":785320,"uid":49391,"like":324,"dislike":4,"score":320,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:22:36.000Z","msg":"奇幻逆緣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:23:50.000Z","msg":"你覺得佢大個左個樣會變返後生?"},{"pid":"346c02d9f1b93fe1575635b3f03943fb10c66781","tid":785320,"uid":132587,"like":230,"dislike":13,"score":217,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"拍童夢奇緣唔洗化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://mypaper.pchome.com.tw/show/article/kaohsiung/A1307471230\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.